'''2014年美國大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2014 United States Grand Prix}}）是[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]在2014年11月2日舉辦的賽事。比賽總計56圈，於[[美国|美国]][[德克萨斯|德克萨斯]][[奥斯丁|奥斯丁]]的[[美洲賽道|美洲賽道]]舉行。<ref name="final wmsc">{{cite web|url=http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-3|title=World Motor Sport Council|date=2013-12-04|accessdate=2014-09-23|work=FIA.com|publisher=[[FIA|FIA]]|archive-date=2013-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207060641/http://www.fia.com/news/world-motor-sport-council-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>這是[[2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的第17場分站賽事，且是第3屆舉辦於[[奥斯丁|奥斯丁]]的[[美國大獎賽|美國大獎賽]]，及第63屆世界錦標賽賽事。

這場賽事僅有18輛賽車上場。這是自[[2005年摩納哥大獎賽|2005年摩納哥大獎賽]]後，上場車輛最少的一次。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/marussia%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bgp-070200536.html|title=Marussia車隊將不會出席美國GP|date=2014-10-27|accessdate=2014-11-02|author=Chumiya|publisher=Racingnet|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102155844/https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/marussia%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bgp-070200536.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>本場賽事最終由[[劉易斯·漢米爾頓|劉易斯·漢米爾頓]]獲得勝利。<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11204538/Lewis-Hamilton-delivers-swashbuckling-US-Grand-Prix-victory-to-move-closer-to-a-second-drivers-championship.html|title=Lewis Hamilton delivers swashbuckling US Grand Prix victory to move closer to a second drivers' championship|date=2014-11-02|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2014-11-03|archive-date=2014-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103150215/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/11204538/Lewis-Hamilton-delivers-swashbuckling-US-Grand-Prix-victory-to-move-closer-to-a-second-drivers-championship.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2818052/Lewis-Hamilton-claims-10th-win-season-ahead-Nico-Rosberg-Mercedes-lead-United-States-Grand-Prix-way.html|title=Lewis Hamilton wins 10th race of the season ahead of Nico Rosberg as Mercedes lead United States Grand Prix all the way|date=2014-11-02|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2014-11-03|archive-date=2014-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103013637/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/formulaone/article-2818052/Lewis-Hamilton-claims-10th-win-season-ahead-Nico-Rosberg-Mercedes-lead-United-States-Grand-Prix-way.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==賽事簡報==
===背景===
====輪胎====
[[一級方程式輪胎|輪胎]]供應商[[倍耐力|倍耐力]]宣布他們將提供各隊白色中性胎作為較硬的首選胎，以及黃色軟胎作為備選胎，與前兩屆在奧斯丁所提供的硬胎與中性胎有所不同。<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/10/16460.html |title=Pirelli reveal tyre choices for final three Grands Prix 08 Oct 2014 |accessdate=2014-10-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014232157/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/10/16460.html |archivedate=2014-10-14 }}</ref>

====車隊變更====
[[卡特漢姆車隊|卡特漢姆]]及[[瑪魯西亞車隊|瑪魯西亞車隊]]兩隊在面臨財務危機後，獲准缺席此次的大獎賽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/29765039|title=Caterham 'allowed' to miss US and Brazil GPs by Bernie Ecclestone|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-10-21|website=bbc.com|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2014-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024205131/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/29765039|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/29770496|title=Marussia and Caterham to miss US Grand Prix|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-10-25|website=bbc.com|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912221845/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/29770496|dead-url=no}}</ref>隨著18輛賽車的出賽，排位賽的程序也進行了修訂。在第一與第二階段將分別淘汰最慢的四輛車，而非原先的六輛。第三階段也是最後一個階段則維持不變，將決定最終前十名排位的車輛。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/10/16537.html |title=Qualifying format revised due to Caterham, Marussia absence |publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited |date=2014-10-30 |website=Formula1.com |accessdate=2014-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030234315/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/10/16537.html |archivedate=2014-10-30 }}</ref>

====減少空氣阻力系統====
國際汽聯選擇延用前兩年賽事所使用的[[減少空氣阻力系統|減少空氣阻力系統]]區域，第一個位於11與12號彎間的長直道，第二個則位於20至1號彎間的起跑線直道。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/318072/|title=United States GP retains two DRS zones|publisher=JHED Media BV|date=2014-10-26|website=gpupdate.net|accessdate=2014-10-28|archive-date=2014-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029045817/http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/318072/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====虛擬安全車（VSC）====
在周五的兩階段自由練習賽後，國際汽聯為了降低像是[[儒勒·比安奇|儒勒·比安奇]]在[[2014年日本大獎賽|2014年日本大獎賽]]所發生的嚴重事故與傷亡的風險，首次測試這項新系統。目標是讓車手在儀表板顯示資料的輔助下，強迫車手在事故區降低大約35%的速度。車手們也認同這是一項有價值的系統，不過還有待調整改善。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.planet-f1.com/driver/18227/9543443/Alonso-Still-work-to-be-done-on-VSC |title=Alonso: Still work to be done on VSC |publisher=PlanetF1.com |date=2014-10-31 |accessdate=2014-11-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102111855/http://www.planet-f1.com/driver/18227/9543443/Alonso-Still-work-to-be-done-on-VSC |archivedate=2014-11-02 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%8B%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BB%8A%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E8%AE%9A%E8%B3%9E-075100412.html|title=車手對虛擬安全車測試表示讚賞|publisher=Racingnet|author=Chumiya|date=2014-11-01|accessdate=2014-11-02|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102160702/https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%8B%E5%B0%8D%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BB%8A%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E8%AE%9A%E8%B3%9E-075100412.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===排位賽===
[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]因為隊友[[劉易斯·漢米爾頓|劉易斯·漢米爾頓]]受困於煞車鎖死的問題，成功從他手中奪下個人本季的第九次桿位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16556.html |title=Qualifying-rapid Rosberg beats Hamilton to pole |publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited |date=2014-11-01 |website=Formula1.com |accessdate=2014-11-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101224237/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16556.html |archivedate=2014-11-01 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9B%B0%E6%93%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%85%9E%E8%BB%8A%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8Chamilton%E6%8B%B1%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%93%E5%87%BA%E7%AB%BF%E4%BD%8D-055000169.html|title=困擾於煞車問題Hamilton拱手讓出竿位|publisher=Racingnet|author=Chumiya|date=2014-11-02|accessdate=2014-11-02|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102155912/https://tw.autos.yahoo.com/news/%E5%9B%B0%E6%93%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%85%9E%E8%BB%8A%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8Chamilton%E6%8B%B1%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%93%E5%87%BA%E7%AB%BF%E4%BD%8D-055000169.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

